response.overview: Ren MacCormack is transplanted from Boston to the small southern town of Bomont where loud music and dancing are prohibited. Not one to bow to the status quo, Ren challenges the ban, revitalizing the town and falling in love with the minister’s troubled daughter Ariel in the process.
response.tagline: There comes a time to cut loose
response.title: Footloose

titles.title: เต้นนี้เพื่อเธอ
